We will continue this with global brands. Big ones. Several have agreed already, more will come. I wish we could name some, but it's a bit too early.

‚Ä®Maybe get in now, if you like the idea of voting, working with brands, with the potential for a nice active and passive income.

This week, we did a casual AMA with a senior director from MONSTER ENERGY in our discord for a start.

We are now setting up working groups with our users, where they work with the brand and form the brands' NFT experience. 

We embed our users and we reward them.

We do not have any influencers. We did not accept investors yet, in fact we politely declined several. 
That will change soon, but we want them to understand that this is about community first. 
Not just about money.

We are serious when we say: ‚Ä®
Our mission is not hype. We are here to stay.‚Ä®
A top 3 NFT platform in five years. 
‚Ä®Not next month, not this summer. 
Our gameplay is bigger.

Talking about the team: We have handpicked a world class group so far. ‚Ä®Senior people from some of the most successful companies in blockchain tech, on the frontend and product side of things former senior employees from Google, Coca Cola, Adidas and many more. https://t.co/w3OQ5dCK1R

You can switch between both worlds anytime, fast and easy. 

Our tech team is growing fast and we are headhunting senior people from both the crypto world and some of the biggest companies in the world. Expect the best platform UI/UX you have seen so far.

Fr0ntierX is  a marketplace with two chains. 

One is based on Ethereum, the second is one that is more convenient for brands. Opening the possibility for big airdrops without gas costs. Enabling inexperienced retail people to have their own wallet. 

Simple. Easy. Approachable.

Our biggest motivation for this was to combine web 2.0 with the incredible power and communities of web 3.0.

To integrate users with ownership, without making it impossible for Web 2.0 brands to enter the space.
And that's not as easy as it sounds. https://t.co/JxjlP0C6c0

LooksRare, X2Y2, fully decentralised ones, of course rarible, etc.‚Ä® - Coinbase is launching soon and other big players are entering the market, too. 

However, eight months ago we thought that there is still room for something new. Something special.

Fr0ntierX is an NFT marketplace and issuance platform. ‚Ä®And over time it is way more. 

First of all: why another one?
‚Ä®‚Ä®Its not a big revelation to you that OpenSea - still the no1 platform - does have issues. ‚Ä®And yes, there are many new NFT marketplaces out there. https://t.co/VLXmkxAaDR

I don't like long threadsüßµbut it is the time to do one. 

I am one of the founders of @Fr0ntierX and want to share with you what it is and why it is important...
